# Number letter Counts - Pseudocoding

1. Read the input from the user and store it in the valriable n 
2. Use FOR LOOP to get the each digit from the input
3. Use IF ELSE staements to count the letter of each words and the add them to the variable value
    to get the count of letters of numbers in word form, group them based on the len of the words 
4. Print the value
